From bbae011803a0371cf9fe2532491ef1e980c06f60 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Debasish Biswas <debasishbsws.dev@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Feb 2026 10:38:05 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] Patch istio WORKSPACE to add patches to the vendored envoy dependency.

0001-envoy-remove-sysroot.patch removes the glibc sysroot so the build uses
Wolfi system headers with the system-installed LLVM 18.

0002-envoy-use-system-yq.patch uses system yq instead of the Bazel-downloaded
yq to avoid architecture-specific download failures on amd64.

0003-fix-go-deps.patch fixes missing Go deps in Gazelle-generated BUILD files
for afero v1.10.0 and lyft/protoc-gen-star v2.

Signed-off-by: Debasish Biswas <debasishbsws.dev@gmail.com>
---
 WORKSPACE | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/WORKSPACE b/WORKSPACE
index cd7515d..4169a61 100644
--- a/WORKSPACE
+++ b/WORKSPACE
@@ -44,6 +44,9 @@ http_archive(
         "//bazel:0003-network-fix-crash-in-getAddressWithPort-when-called-.patch",
         "//bazel:0004-fix-multivalue-header-bypass-in-rbac.patch",
         "//bazel:0005-ratelimit-fix-a-bug-where-response-phase-limit-may-r.patch",
+        "//:0001-envoy-remove-sysroot.patch",
+        "//:0002-envoy-use-system-yq.patch",
+        "//:0003-fix-go-deps.patch",
     ],
     patch_args = ["-p1"],
 )
